title: John Anderson- Eye Of A Hurricane
description:
"Eye Of A Hurricane,"  was released in 1984 . One of John&#039;s best albums in my opinion.
 Even in the early days of John&#039;s career you can hear that something extra in his voice. The song&#039;s subject matter is relatable to just about everyone who has ever been in a relationship.
